  "texts": [
    "The sigmoid activation function is applied in the last layer, which produces a scalar output in the range [0, 1]:",
    "We use the cross-entropy loss for the training of the neural network:",
    "where the binary label y i indicates whether the input gene is the true target of the input compound.",
    "The quantities of neurons in the hidden layers are hyperparameters.",
    "In our experiment, we used 2048 and 512 neurons for the Dense 1 and Dense 2 layers, respectively."
